FACTORY_DEF {*} TeeFactory    FACTORY_NAME { AttributeExposer }    INPUT  FEATURE_TYPE LOOKUP_TABLES_READER_NG_Output    OUTPUT { FEATURE_TYPE AttributeExposer_OUTPUT          }
